title: MALCOLM IN THE MIDDLE: SEASON 1 - SEASON 7 - [ENG][2000-2006] -
description: Malcolm in the Middle is a seven-time Emmy-winning,[1] one-time Grammy-winning[1] and seven-time Golden Globe-nominated[1] critically-acclaimed American sitcom created by Linwood Boomer for the Fox Network. The series was first broadcast on January 9, 2000, and ended its six-and-a-half-year run on May 14, 2006, after seven seasons. It now can be viewed on the FX Network (United States), YTV (Canada) and local networks in syndication.
